<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.188342>
    dc:description "FIGURES 3 – 10. Neopantopsalis quasimodo n. sp., male. 3. Lateral view of body showing chelicerae and pedipalps (QM S 2481, holotype). 4. Lateral view of body with appendages removed (QM S 2481, holotype). 5. Cheliceral fingers, frontal view (QM S 74301). 6. Femur to tibia of right leg I, dorsal view (QM S 2481, holotype). 7. Total penis, right lateral view (QM S 2488). 8. Glans, right lateral view (QM S 2488). 9. Glans of same male, ventral view (QM S 2488). 10. Glans of different male, ventral view (QM S 74301). Scale bars for Figs. 3 – 6 = 1 mm; Fig. 7 = 0.5 mm; Figs. 8 – 10 = 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/188342/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.188349>
    dc:description "FIGURES 33 – 36. Neopantopsalis thaumatopoios n. sp., male (QM S 2850). 33. Dorsal view of body. 34. Lateral view of body with anterior limbs. 35. Tip of penis, lateral view. 36. Tip of penis, ventral view. Scale bars for Figs. 33 and 34 = 1 mm; Figs. 35 and 36 = 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/188349/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

